    "Bug Detection.",
    "Intelligent Code Analysis Agent (ICAA) [35] is used for bug detection in static code analysis.",
    "The agents have access to tools like web search, static analysis, and code retrieval tools.",
    "A Report Agent generates bug reports, while a False Positive Pruner Agent refines these reports to reduce false positives."
